This angular application should be using bootstrap and atomic css.
The amount of custom css needs to be minimized to the extent possible.
The typescript code and in general the code should be easy to understand and maintain.
The code should have proper logging and comments.
Use ngrx based state-management wherver it is required. ue it spraingly for absolutely necessary use cases.
Organize code into feature modules and shared modules.
Use lazy loading for large modules to improve performance.
Keep components small and focused on a single responsibility.
Avoid directly manipulating the DOM; use Renderer2.
Use HttpClient interceptors for auth tokens and error handling.
